Operations

findUnique

Find zero or one User

// Get one User
const user = await prisma.user.findUnique({
  where: {
    // ... provide filter here
  }
})

Input

Name Type Required
where UserWhereUniqueInput Yes

Output

Type: User
Required: No
List: No

findFirst

Find first User

// Get one User
const user = await prisma.user.findFirst({
  where: {
    // ... provide filter here
  }
})

Input

Name Type Required
where UserWhereInput No
orderBy UserOrderByWithRelationAndSearchRelevanceInput[] | UserOrderByWithRelationAndSearchRelevanceInput No
cursor UserWhereUniqueInput No
take Int No
skip Int No
distinct UserScalarFieldEnum | UserScalarFieldEnum[] No

Output

Type: User
Required: No
List: No

findMany

// Get all User
